{
  "stem": "18450.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was somebody in the-- the Polish Senate, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, if I say, I know from remember just things we used to said.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could feel it that something's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if they-- the invasion came in, we went away to our little village and we stayed there about a week till things starts cooling down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they said that's not the Germans, but the Russians going came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then they came back to our house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[POLISH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know how you spell it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it wasn't in the newspapers so much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the mouth-to-mouth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People who-- I mean, they didn't know so much what went on, like the Kristallnacht, or so.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't hear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe people who were older or more knowledgeable of those things, they probably hear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you could smell the air wasn't clean anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a neighbor who was a [INAUDIBLE] guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wore glasses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he went out one night, and they broke his glasses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everybody thought it's somebody who's just, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nobody were thinking about what happened, that this is going to be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, absolutely no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this time, the Russians were there in--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In September '41.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The were in our city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took-- this part of Poland went to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other part were the-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So a lot of the people came to our city from the other part, from large-- from all the other cities they came to-- to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "99% Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And life was rough, and it was really, if you didn't have connections, from food or whatever, everyone, like no more stores.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So every storekeeper tried to accumulate some shoes and this.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
